A thin-walled tube, [`[$l]`] [`m`] long, [`OD = [$od]`] [`mm`], [`ID = [$id]`] [`mm`], [`G = [$g]`] [`MPa`] is fixed at one end. A torque, [`T = [$torque]`] [`Nm`] acts at the other end. Calculate the angle of rotation [`\phi`].  
_Hint: The torque causes shearing of the tube wall_. 

[`\phi=`] [____]{"$phi"}[`^{\circ}`] 

